trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: 包含 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 物件的集合。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別無法被繼承。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection> class allows you to programmatically access a collection of <xref:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping> objects.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection>類別可讓您以程式設計方式存取的集合<xref:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping>物件。

trans-unit.source: The collection can be accessed with either the key or the index.
trans-unit.target: 可以使用索引鍵或索引存取集合。

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 建立 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the virtual directory path.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.String" />，包含虛擬目錄路徑。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: Adds a <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 將 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 物件加入至 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 執行個體。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="mapping" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="mapping" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="virtualDirectory" /> already exists in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="virtualDirectory" /> 已存在於 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 中。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> is read-only.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 是唯讀的。

trans-unit.source: Returns a string array that contains all the keys in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 傳回含有 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 執行個體中所有索引鍵的字串陣列。

trans-unit.source: A string array that contains all the keys in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 字串陣列，含有 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 執行個體中所有的索引鍵。

trans-unit.source: Clears all <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> objects from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 將所有的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 物件從 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 執行個體中清除。

trans-unit.source: A one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" /> that is the destination of the elements copied from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 一維 <see cref="T:System.Array" />，是從 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 複製項目的目的端。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Array" /> must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Array" /> 必須有以零為起始的索引。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: <c>array</c> 中以零起始的索引，複製作業從此處開始。

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> collection to a compatible one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" />, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: 從目標陣列的指定之索引開始，將整個 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 集合複製到相容的一維 <see cref="T:System.Array" />。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.Array.Length" /> property of <paramref name="array" /> is less than the value of <see cref="P:System.Collections.Specialized.NameObjectCollectionBase.Count" /> plus <paramref name="index" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> 的 <see cref="P:System.Array.Length" /> 屬性小於 <see cref="P:System.Collections.Specialized.NameObjectCollectionBase.Count" /> 加上 <paramref name="index" /> 的值。

trans-unit.source: Gets the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> collection element.
trans-unit.target: 取得指定的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 集合項目。

trans-unit.source: An integer value that specifies a particular <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object within the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 指定 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 內特定 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 物件的整數值。

trans-unit.source: Gets the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> collection element at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 取得位於指定索引處的指定 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 集合項目。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> element at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 在指定索引的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 項目。

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the name of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 包含 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 物件名稱的字串。

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> collection element based on the specified virtual-directory name.
trans-unit.target: 根據指定的虛擬目錄名稱，取得或設定 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 集合項目。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> element based on the specified virtual-directory name.
trans-unit.target: 根據指定之虛擬目錄名稱的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 項目。

trans-unit.source: An integer value that specifies a particular <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object within the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 指定 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 內特定 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 物件的整數值。

trans-unit.source: Gets the key of the entry at the specified index of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 取得 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 執行個體指定索引處之項目的索引鍵。

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the name of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 包含 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 物件名稱的字串。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: An integer value that specifies a particular <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object within the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 指定 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 內特定 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 物件的整數值。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object at the specified index location.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定在指定索引位置的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the name of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 包含 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 物件名稱的字串。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object based on the specified virtual directory name.
trans-unit.target: 根據指定的虛擬目錄名稱，取得或設定 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the name of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 包含 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 物件名稱的字串。

trans-unit.source: Removes a <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 從 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 執行個體中移除 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: An integer value that specifies a particular <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object within the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 指定 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 內特定 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 物件的整數值。

trans-unit.source: Removes a <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object at the specified index from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 從 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 的指定索引處移除 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 物件。
